{"tid":1650023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對家發現新分化手段","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:39:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T19:47:48.000Z","uid":25663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb076fdd5808b83c10438a6edf43eaaf274d9d6","tid":1650023,"uid":25663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:39:11.000Z","msg":"就係係發夢現實攪返2014年個啲嘉年華<br />\n即刻全世界圍屌，又割蓆仲報埋串<br />\n唔係撐佢，都知哩個唔係好風氣，場合唔岩<br />\n但可唔可以試下好似對家咁冷處理下？<br />\n二百萬人個個唔同，實有人會做得出唔同嘅野<br />\n我地嘅槍口一致對出好無<br />\n<br />\n黎緊對家一定會做返類似嘅野去分化我地，嘗試瓦解運動<br />\n<br />\n哩次係我地嘅一次機會，去學下點處理自己人嘅問題，我地多啲提點，唔要割蓆好無<br />\n<br />\n同樣地，我地每人做每一件事，講話前都諗下會有咩影響先好無<br />\n<br />\n唔好再犯5年前嘅錯，要做到5年前做唔到嘅野<br />\n<br />\n幾多人都好，有同樣嘅立場，有各自嘅想法，但都可以團結咁一齊保護我城<br />\n兄弟爬山，互相扶持，永不放棄"},{"pid":"d9393382db242209504f0b341759d800710adbb8","tid":1650023,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:42:29.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71rUgoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71rUgoF.jpg&h=dfc19a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmG1FQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmG1FQk.jpg&h=16c44ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jk7sBoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJk7sBoG.png&h=6f2b4d34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oue6RW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOue6RW2.jpg&h=f95c8cc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a71fe769778f386fb5f1afb0b0c7a725c4f1153b","tid":1650023,"uid":312412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:44:26.000Z","msg":"［警告］唔好再比人分化！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1650021\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1650021</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3f9d628e6616aae7446597fbb26865fdc4a01fec","tid":1650023,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-1